    "longBusinessSummary": "An Phat Bioplastics Joint Stock Company, together with its subsidiaries, produces and trades in plastic products in Vietnam, Singapore, the United States, Korea, and internationally. The company offers plastic packaging products; compostable, krafted paper, food, garbage, and shopping/fashion bags; PE liners; stretch and agriculture films; and draw tape and plastic bags, gloves, knives, forks, and straws under the AnEco brand name. It also provides additives and limestone powders; develops industrial park infrastructure; trades in plastic beads and other plastic products; offers transportation of goods by road, coastal, and ocean freight; manufactures engineering and household plastics, and molds and mechanical machining products; leases factories; sub-leases industrial land; and manufactures and trades in plastic interior decoration. The company was formerly known as An Phat Plastic And Green Environment Joint Stock Company and changed its name to An Phat Bioplastics Joint Stock Company in April 2019. An Phat Bioplastics Joint Stock Company was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Hai Duong, Vietnam. An Phat Bioplastics Joint Stock Company operates as a subsidiary of An Phat Holdings Joint Stock Company.",
